snippet.title: TimeWarp - City Gameplay
snippet.description:
DATE: 8th June 2010, 1:20 PM
LOCATION: Welport City, North America
GOAL: Find and infiltrate mercenary submarine, find Time Crystal

Gameplay of the city chapter for my HL1 mod TimeWarp!
Hope you like it!
NOTE: Everything you see here is a work in progress and subject to change, especially the placeholders, like the voicelines.

Check out the demo: https://www.moddb.com/mods/timewarp/downloads/timewarp-demo-v10
Join the discord server for frequent updates: https://discord.gg/PSSSzmj2JR
